  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate safety, tolerability and performance of the CyclaPlex
      implant, a button and suture type implant device and instruments for the correction of the
      first inter metatarsal angle in subjects suffering from Hallux Valgus deformity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
